        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer16136302&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer16136302" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16783427386137473260">A lower class woman eventually marries her upper class would-be-rapist. This novel somehow manages to be more misogynistic and offensive than the collected works of de Sade. It&apos;s also boring.</span>
  <span id="freeText16783427386137473260" style="display:none">A lower class woman eventually marries her upper class would-be-rapist. This novel somehow manages to be more misogynistic and offensive than the collected works of de Sade. It's also boring.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16783427386137473260" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

